RECOMMENDATIONS & FIXES
Immediate Actions Required
1. iOS Safari Compatibility
/* Fix for navigation overlap */
@media screen and (max-width: 375px) {
    .navbar-brand {
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-right: 10px;
    }
    .navbar-toggler {
        margin-left: auto;
    }
}

/* Fix for form validation */
.form-control:invalid {
    border-color: #dc3545;
    -webkit-appearance: none;
}
2. Android Mobile Improvements
/* Improve hamburger menu visibility */
.navbar-toggler {
    background-color: rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
    min-width: 44px;
    min-height: 44px;
}

/* Fix product title truncation */
.product-title {
    display: -webkit-box;
    -webkit-line-clamp: 2;
    -webkit-box-orient: vertical;
    overflow: hidden;
    line-height: 1.4;
    max-height: 2.8em;
}
3. Touch Target Optimization
/* Ensure minimum touch target size */
.btn, .btn-sm, button, input[type="button"] {
    min-width: 44px;
    min-height: 44px;
    padding: 8px 12px;
}

/* Improve touch spacing */
@media (max-width: 767px) {
    .btn + .btn {
        margin-left: 8px;
        margin-top: 8px;
    }
}
Performance Optimizations
1. Image Optimization
•	Implement responsive images with srcset and sizes
•	Use WebP format with JPEG fallback
•	Add lazy loading for below-the-fold images
•	Optimize image compression (target <100KB per image)
<img src="product-small.jpg"
     srcset="product-small.jpg 480w,
             product-medium.jpg 800w,
             product-large.jpg 1200w"
     sizes="(max-width: 480px) 100vw,
            (max-width: 800px) 50vw,
            25vw"
     alt="Product Name"
     loading="lazy">
2. JavaScript Optimization
•	Split JavaScript bundles by route
•	Implement code splitting for better loading
•	Use service worker for caching
•	Minify and compress JavaScript files
Responsive Design Fixes
1. Container Overflow Fix
/* Prevent horizontal overflow */
* {
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

.container-fluid {
    overflow-x: hidden;
    padding-left: 15px;
    padding-right: 15px;
}

@media (max-width: 576px) {
    .container, .container-fluid {
        padding-left: 10px;
        padding-right: 10px;
    }
}
2. Flexible Grid System
/* Improve product grid responsiveness */
.product-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 1rem;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));
}

@media (max-width: 576px) {
    .product-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(150px, 1fr));
        gap: 0.5rem;
    }
}
Browser-Specific Fixes
1. Firefox Improvements
/* Fix Firefox filter animation */
.filter-container {
    will-change: transform;
    transform: translateZ(0);
}

/* Firefox product card spacing */
@-moz-document url-prefix() {
    .product-card {
        margin-bottom: 18px;
    }
}
2. Safari Enhancements
/* Safari autofill styling */
input:-webkit-autofill {
    -webkit-box-shadow: 0 0 0 1000px white inset;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: #333;
}

/* Safari search input */
input[type="search"] {
    -webkit-appearance: none;
    appearance: none;
}

